269
00:15:14,410 --> 00:15:15,940
—Good morning.
—Good morning.

270
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:23,180
A red letter?

271
00:15:28,890 --> 00:15:31,230
Lately,

272
00:15:31,290 --> 00:15:32,730
we've been struggling

273
