with several things.

274
00:15:33,930 --> 00:15:36,530
I'd like this season

275
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:37,900
to be completely released

276
00:15:37,970 --> 00:15:39,400
with Amazon, though.

277
00:15:40,540 --> 00:15:42,300
