283
00:15:49,610 --> 00:15:51,180
Sure am. It's been eight years already.

284
00:15:51,350 --> 00:15:53,480
I don't really remember.

285
00:15:53,850 --> 00:15:56,450
I'd say his main attribute would be...

286
00:15:57,090 --> 00:15:58,490
his high potential.

287
00:15:58,750 --> 00:16:00,990
I think he'll be able to stand high levels of stress, too.

288
00:16:02,460 --> 00:16:05,160
He can make things as chaotic as he wants.

289
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:07,830
So they want me to go there and make a mess, huh?

290
