For real.

538
00:27:49,200 --> 00:27:54,970
Okay, everyone! Please give me the money!

539
00:27:55,970 --> 00:27:57,540
For real...

540
00:27:57,770 --> 00:27:59,510
Oh come on...

541
00:27:59,570 --> 00:28:00,910
I want this!

542
00:28:00,980 --> 00:28:03,210
—I know, right?
—I really want it!

543
00:28:03,280 --> 00:28:05,610
I can't count everything in detail, but I trust you.

544
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:06,680
One million.
One million...

545
00:28:06,750 --> 00:28:08,350
Okay, here we have 5 million.

546
00:28:09,020 --> 00:28:10,280
That's amazing.

547
00:28:10,350 --> 00:28:11,820
That's tight.

548
00:28:11,890 --> 00:28:16,890
It's pretty flashy.
Kind of excessive.

549
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:19,560
By the way, Chance. That's a lot of money, huh?

550
00:28:19,630 --> 00:28:21,460
First time I've seen something like it.

551
00:28:21,630 --> 00:28:24,000
Okay, there it is.

552
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:25,270
So I work in construction, right?

553
00:28:25,330 --> 00:28:27,130
Yeah, construction.

554
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:28,940
