680
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:44,820
It was the fastest ever, while we were just raising the curtain.

681
00:33:44,890 --> 00:33:46,490
-So what now?
-Yeah, yeah, you're right.

682
00:33:46,550 --> 00:33:48,490
Are you really okay with that?

683
00:33:48,820 --> 00:33:50,690
It's a yellow for now.

684
00:33:50,760 --> 00:33:52,930
That was a yellow.

685
00:33:52,990 --> 00:33:55,300
Alright! Now we're getting into it!

686
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:56,960
Never imagined someone would laugh at that, though!

687
00:34:00,130 --> 00:34:02,400
Not on the streets!

688
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:03,940
No way, yeah!

689
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:05,740
Alright, alright.

690
00:34:05,810 --> 00:34:06,940
What have you been doing all this time?

691
00:34:17,050 --> 00:34:19,220
Sukkera Kecchi!!

